311
00:22:38,442 --> 00:22:41,282
I haven't thought that far. I'm sorry.

312
00:22:41,508 --> 00:22:42,962
Forget it. It's already done.

313
00:22:45,608 --> 00:22:47,015
But next time,

314
00:22:47,559 --> 00:22:50,562
