323
00:23:17,979 --> 00:23:18,979
Okay.

324
00:23:19,060 --> 00:23:22,642
We have to get Mr. Chat's heart from Suraphaet Chonburi University Hospital

325
00:23:22,723 --> 00:23:24,305
