00:38:06,072 --> 00:38:07,362
Mata.

479
00:38:07,794 --> 00:38:08,882
Mata.

480
00:38:09,042 --> 00:38:10,242
Mata.

481
00:38:28,059 --> 00:38:29,322
Mata.

