618
00:49:56,411 --> 00:49:57,802
How did it get up there?

619
00:50:00,018 --> 00:50:02,018
How did Konmek get up there?

620
00:50:02,208 --> 00:50:03,962
It ran away from another big dog.

621
00:50:04,076 --> 00:50:06,362
