639
00:51:09,898 --> 00:51:11,138
Konmek!

640
00:51:21,997 --> 00:51:24,202
Yeah!

641
00:51:24,402 --> 00:51:25,605
You're so awesome!

642
00:51:25,708 --> 00:51:27,082
Thank you.

643
00:51:33,958 --> 00:51:35,153
Do you like dogs?

644
00:51:37,282 --> 00:51:38,562
It's a frequency wave.

645
00:51:39,842 --> 00:51:42,202
