652
00:52:00,722 --> 00:52:02,002
Well...

653
00:52:02,362 --> 00:52:05,782
It's good that you have kindness and sympathy for patients.

654
00:52:06,722 --> 00:52:08,122
However,

655
00:52:08,332 --> 00:52:10,332
