657
00:52:18,616 --> 00:52:21,456
If you want to be a good doctor, there's still a lot you need to learn.

658
00:52:25,273 --> 00:52:26,322
Got it.

659
00:52:26,438 --> 00:52:27,642
There's a lot I need to learn.

660
00:52:39,194 --> 00:52:40,602
