685
00:54:27,980 --> 00:54:29,402
I...

686
00:54:29,908 --> 00:54:32,122
I'm fine. There's nothing wrong with me, though.

687
00:54:39,130 --> 00:54:41,422
You look like Dr. Mummim.

688
00:54:44,799 --> 00:54:47,482
